Suggested installation method

Dependencies (Ubuntu package names):
	libgee-0.8-dev
	libgee-0.8-2
	valac-0.30 (or newer)

Optional Features
	gobject-introspection
	libgirepository
	libgladeui-dev

Assuming that cmake and all dependencies are installed, run:
	mkdir build
	cd build
	cmake ..
	make
	sudo make install
